---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Our Story | YourHQ" 
  description="Friends first. Business partners second. Here to help you own your digital space."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="bg-paper min-h-screen">
    
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-20 border-b border-carbon bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
            
            <!-- Header Text -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-7">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-8">
                    Two Mates. <br/>
                    <span class="text-signal">One Mission.</span>
                </h1>
                <div class="max-w-xl border-l-4 border-carbon pl-8 py-2">
                    <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-carbon">
                        Friends first. Business partners second. Here to help you own your digital space.
                    </h2>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Header Image: Laughter/Warmth -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-5">
                <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100 border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500 overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
                    <img
                        src="/nic-lian-laugh.webp"
                        alt="Nic and Lian laughing together"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 1: HOW YOURHQ STARTED -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 leading-relaxed text-lg text-carbon/90 space-y-8">
            
            <div class="mb-12">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-signal mb-2 block">How YourHQ Started</span>
                <p class="font-medium text-xl">
                    Here's a stat that stuck: only 53% of small to medium businesses in New Zealand have a website.
                </p>
                <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-carbon mt-4">Half. In 2025.</p>
            </div>

            <p>
                I kept thinking about it. I watched friends build up profiles on Instagram and Facebook — years of work, thousands of followers, their whole customer base — and then poof. Banned. Hacked. Algorithm changed. Everything gone.
            </p>
            <p>
                All that work. All those contacts. Just... vanished.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-carbon shadow-sm my-8">
                <p class="italic text-lg">
                    "I'm also the kind of person who checks websites before I hire anyone. If I'm picking between two tradies and one's got a beautiful website? I go with that tradie. Every time. It's not rational — but it's real."
                </p>
            </div>

            <p>
                When I started learning to code for my Master's, I kept coming back to this question: <strong>How do I actually get these business owners online?</strong> Not another DIY tool they'll never finish. A system that does the hard part for them.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-carbon">And honestly? I think about my dad.</h3>
            <p>
                He ran a small business — <em>Maungi Tanks</em>. He's not with us anymore. But I imagine what it would've been like to build him a website. To see his face when he saw himself on the internet for the first time.
            </p>
            <p>
                He would have loved it. It would have made him proud.
            </p>
            
            <div class="border-l-4 border-signal pl-6 py-2 mt-8">
                <p class="font-bold text-xl text-carbon mb-2">That's why YourHQ exists.</p>
                <p>For the tradies. The salon owners. The consultants. The small business people who are brilliant at what they do — but never got around to the website part.</p>
                <p class="mt-4">I want to give them what I wish I could've given my dad.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2 & 3: MEET THE TEAM -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-16 text-center">Meet The Team</h2>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start">
                
                <!-- LIAN -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-100 border border-carbon shadow-hard relative overflow-hidden mb-6 group">
                         <img 
                            src="/lian-headshot.webp" 
                            alt="Lian Passmore" 
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" 
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-carbon">Lian</h3>
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">Founder & Lead Developer</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-lg text-carbon/90 space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            15 years helping people communicate better — building learning experiences, designing systems, translating complexity into clarity.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            When I started building AI agents for my Master's, I accidentally taught myself to code. If I can build web apps... why not build websites?
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Taking someone's story and translating it into digital form.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-paper p-4 border-l-2 border-carbon">
                            <span class="font-bold block mb-1">What I bring:</span>
                            Enterprise infrastructure. I handle the builds, the tech, the design — making sure your website sounds like you.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- NIC -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-100 border border-carbon shadow-hard relative overflow-hidden mb-6 group">
                        <img
                            src="/nic-headshot.webp"
                            alt="Nic"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-carbon">Nic</h3>
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">Business Development Manager</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-lg text-carbon/90 space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            I'm Nic — your first point of contact.
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-bold">
                            I didn't just join YourHQ. I used YourHQ.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Lian asked that morning — I'd been wrestling with Wix. She asked me a few questions, went away, and built me a website that looked like my business.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Building a website was my barrier to market. Blocker gone. Now I'm here to help you do the same.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-paper p-4 border-l-2 border-carbon">
                            <span class="font-bold block mb-1">What I bring:</span>
                            I listen, understand where you're coming from, and help you figure out if this is right for you.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 4: FRIENDS FIRST -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-paper border-b border-carbon relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Decorative background element -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-20 -mr-20 w-64 h-64 bg-signal/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-12 text-center">Friends First. Always.</h2>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center mb-16">

                <!-- Polaroid Photos Scatter -->
                <div class="md:col-span-5 order-2 md:order-1 relative">
                    <!-- Rugby Photo - Main/Largest -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-3 shadow-xl transform -rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500 border border-gray-200 relative z-10">
                        <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
                             <img
                                src="/nic-lian-rugby.webp"
                                alt="Nic and Lian playing rugby together"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover sepia-[.3]"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="pt-3 pb-1 text-center font-handwriting text-gray-500 text-sm">
                            The Rugby Days
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Christmas Photo - Top Right -->
                    <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-8 w-32 bg-white p-2 shadow-xl transform rotate-12 hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-500 border border-gray-200 z-20">
                        <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
                            <img
                                src="/nic-lian-xmas.webp"
                                alt="Nic and Lian at Christmas"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="pt-1 pb-1 text-center font-handwriting text-gray-500 text-[10px]">
                            Christmas
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Food Photo - Bottom Left -->
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-32 bg-white p-2 shadow-xl transform -rotate-6 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500 border border-gray-200 z-20">
                        <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
                            <img
                                src="/nic-lian-food.webp"
                                alt="Nic and Lian enjoying food together"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="pt-1 pb-1 text-center font-handwriting text-gray-500 text-[10px]">
                            Good Times
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Narrative Text -->
                <div class="md:col-span-7 order-1 md:order-2 text-lg leading-relaxed text-carbon/90 space-y-6">
                    <p>
                        Mates for over 12 years.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We've been each other's hype girls through every wild idea, every hard season.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Nic was the only person I asked.
                    </p>
                    <p class="font-medium italic">
                        Because we trust each other completely.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center pt-12 mt-12 border-t border-carbon/20">
                <p class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">And that's what you get when you work with us:</p>
                <p class="text-lg">Two people who genuinely care. Who want to see you thrive — not just sell you something.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 5: BEST OF BOTH WORLDS -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-carbon text-paper">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-12 text-white text-center">The Best of Both Worlds</h2>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
                <!-- With Lian -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-sm border border-gray-700 hover:border-signal transition-colors duration-300">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-signal mb-4">With Lian</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">
                        Obsesses over getting your message right. Builds infrastructure that works while you sleep. Won't rest until your website sounds like you.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- With Nic -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-sm border border-gray-700 hover:border-signal transition-colors duration-300">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-signal mb-4">With Nic</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">
                        Makes you feel heard. Answers questions without jargon.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center space-y-4">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">We're not a faceless agency.</p>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-400">We're two Kiwis who believe you deserve to own your digital space.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 6: CTA -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8 text-carbon">Ready to Meet Us?</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-12 text-lg text-carbon/80">
                <p>Questions? Chat with Nic.</p>
                <p>Ready to build? <strong>Let's go.</strong></p>
            </div>

            <div class="inline-block p-1 border-2 border-dashed border-gray-400 rounded-full">
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-signal hover:bg-red-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-12 rounded-full transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-hard">
                    Let's Chat
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>